Upgrade a CRM Analytics App

To upgrade a CRM Analytics app, follow these steps:

* Click the "What's new" link in the banner or the "New version available" link on your app home page.
* Read information about the new version and find the buttons: Upgrade current app and Create new app.
* If you've customized your app, click Create new app to make an app copy based on the new version. Otherwise, click Upgrade current app.
* Review the screen that indicates which assets are impacted by the upgrade.
* Download a file with code for changes made to the app if you've customized it.
* Click Upgrade current app or Create new app to complete the process.

Required user permissions:
Manage CRM Analytics Templated Apps
Edit CRM Analytics Dataflows
title: Upgrading Salesforce CRM Analytics Apps
